It must be really tiring for Mr. Zhang

39
00:03:02,580 --> 00:03:03,820
to lead the team.

40
00:03:03,950 --> 00:03:05,310
They're here mainly for a site inspection.

41
00:03:05,980 --> 00:03:08,470
Talking here

42
00:03:08,470 --> 00:03:09,750
won't achieve anything.

43
00:03:13,030 --> 00:03:14,660
Liuhua, have you prepared the tea?

44
00:03:14,660 --> 00:03:15,190
It's ready.

45
00:03:15,190 --> 00:03:16,660
The delegates will be here anytime.

46
00:03:16,660 --> 00:03:17,630
Don't worry.

47
00:03:19,580 --> 00:03:21,100
Mr. Li,

48
00:03:21,100 --> 00:03:22,260
