49
00:03:23,380 --> 00:03:24,380
You're almost there?

50
00:03:24,630 --> 00:03:26,190
Sure. I'll be right there.

51
00:03:26,470 --> 00:03:27,980
Xiuyu.

52
00:03:29,510 --> 00:03:30,790
It's bad timing,

53
00:03:30,790 --> 00:03:32,350
