75
00:04:15,980 --> 00:04:17,630
She is from our village.

76
00:04:19,100 --> 00:04:20,190
We don't have enough budget

77
00:04:20,470 --> 00:04:22,420
to hire a celebrity.

78
00:04:22,420 --> 00:04:24,380
Nonetheless, the sales have been quite good,

79
00:04:24,380 --> 00:04:25,630
and we're making a very decent profit.

80
00:04:25,910 --> 00:04:27,670
Mr. Zhang, watch your steps.

81
00:04:27,870 --> 00:04:29,700
This is the first inn in the village.

82
00:04:29,700 --> 00:04:30,380
I've heard about it.

83
00:04:30,380 --> 00:04:31,950
The owner of the inn is He Xingfu.

84
00:04:32,780 --> 00:04:34,260
[Xingfu Inn]
You even know her name.

85
00:04:34,260 --> 00:04:36,140
My friend is a writer.

86
00:04:36,310 --> 00:04:37,340
He used to live here.

87
00:04:37,430 --> 00:04:38,220
After he went back,

88
00:04:38,220 --> 00:04:40,780
he couldn't stop praising the inn and its owner.

89
00:04:41,220 --> 00:04:42,780
That made me really curious.

90
00:04:43,340 --> 00:04:45,310
That's why I've always wanted to visit the inn

91
00:04:45,550 --> 00:04:47,190
and meet He Xingfu myself.

92
00:04:47,190 --> 00:04:48,190
You'll see her soon.

93
00:04:48,310 --> 00:04:50,430
[Welcome to Xingfu Inn, fellow judges!]
He Xingfu always strives to do better

94
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:52,075
and has already applied to be a member of the CPC.

95
00:04:53,430 --> 00:04:54,430
Welcome

96
00:04:54,430 --> 00:04:56,020
to Xingfu Inn, sirs.

97
00:04:57,310 --> 00:04:57,870
This way, please.

98
00:04:57,870 --> 00:04:59,310
Sure. This way, please.

99
00:05:01,380 --> 00:05:02,020
This way, please.

100
00:05:02,580 --> 00:05:04,510
After crossing the Bridge of Happiness,
(* "happiness" pronounces as "xingfu")

101
00:05:04,510 --> 00:05:05,990
we'll arrive at the lobby.

102
00:05:06,070 --> 00:05:07,310
In the lobby...

103
00:05:07,310 --> 00:05:07,670
Here.

104
00:05:07,820 --> 00:05:08,670
Watch your steps.

105
00:05:08,820 --> 00:05:09,870
In the lobby,

106
00:05:09,870 --> 00:05:11,380
