107
00:05:11,380 --> 00:05:12,820
and the story wall.

108
00:05:13,190 --> 00:05:15,700
Xiuyu, where is Xingfu?

109
00:05:16,070 --> 00:05:17,900
Why isn't she here to receive the guests?

110
00:05:18,990 --> 00:05:22,020
Xingfu had something important to do,
so she went out.

111
00:05:22,950 --> 00:05:24,020
What is it that's so important?

112
00:05:24,820 --> 00:05:26,340
Is it more important
than receiving the delegates?

113
00:05:26,750 --> 00:05:27,340
It's fine.

114
00:05:27,340 --> 00:05:29,110
Give her a call
and tell her to come here right away.

115
00:05:29,380 --> 00:05:30,990
Xiuyu, I'll call her.

116
00:05:30,990 --> 00:05:33,260
You can show the guests around.

117
00:05:33,380 --> 00:05:34,260
I'll call her.

118
00:05:34,750 --> 00:05:35,780
Sure. Please come in.

119
00:05:35,780 --> 00:05:37,950
This way.

120
00:05:37,950 --> 00:05:39,110
Watch your steps.

121
00:05:42,550 --> 00:05:44,260
Ms. He, thanks to you,

122
00:05:44,260 --> 00:05:45,820
our efficiency has improved significantly.

123
00:05:45,990 --> 00:05:47,190
Thank you for making the trip.

124
00:05:47,190 --> 00:05:48,020
Thanks.

125
00:05:48,020 --> 00:05:48,550
It's part of our job.

126
00:05:48,550 --> 00:05:49,340
Ms. He.

127
00:05:50,580 --> 00:05:51,630
Why are you here?

128
00:05:52,430 --> 00:05:55,020
Aren't the judges visiting the village today
for the inspection?

129
00:05:56,140 --> 00:05:56,820
What's wrong?

130
00:05:57,110 --> 00:05:58,460
Why aren't you working today?

131
00:05:59,380 --> 00:06:01,580
I was on night shift yesterday,
so I'm getting the day off.

132
00:06:02,700 --> 00:06:04,070
Ms. Guo, let me just answer this call.

133
00:06:04,070 --> 00:06:05,820
Please bring Mr. Li and his colleague
to Madam Zhang's place.

134
00:06:06,340 --> 00:06:06,870
Sure.

135
00:06:07,140 --> 00:06:08,510
Li, this way.

136
00:06:08,510 --> 00:06:11,190
Mr. Wan.

137
00:06:11,380 --> 00:06:13,380
Xingfu, where are you?

138
00:06:14,140 --> 00:06:15,340
I'm at Shuiwei Village.

139
00:06:16,190 --> 00:06:17,510
Why are you there?

140
00:06:18,510 --> 00:06:20,630
The delegates are here at the Xingfu Inn,

141
00:06:20,630 --> 00:06:21,780
but you, the owner, are not here.

142
00:06:22,430 --> 00:06:23,870
I've got everything prepared.

143
00:06:24,340 --> 00:06:26,750
Xiuyu will receive the guests
and do the presentation on my behalf.

144
00:06:26,750 --> 00:06:27,670
There will be no difference.

145
00:06:27,670 --> 00:06:28,900
It's different.

146
00:06:31,070 --> 00:06:32,900
Mr. Zhang said this himself.

147
00:06:32,900 --> 00:06:34,190
He wants to meet you.

148
00:06:34,190 --> 00:06:35,630
Can't you just do it for the greater good?

149
00:06:36,020 --> 00:06:37,580
This is a major event.

150
00:06:37,580 --> 00:06:38,820
It will affect the entire village.

151
00:06:38,820 --> 00:06:40,310
It's a collective honor.

152
00:06:40,460 --> 00:06:41,870
Don't you know what to do now?

153
00:06:42,110 --> 00:06:43,550
Get back here now,

154
00:06:43,550 --> 00:06:44,550
or you'll have to bear the consequences.

155
00:06:56,260 --> 00:06:56,900
Liuhua.

156
00:06:57,670 --> 00:06:58,870
Keep this.

157
00:06:58,870 --> 00:07:00,140
We can use it again.

158
00:07:00,140 --> 00:07:00,670
Sure.

159
00:07:03,220 --> 00:07:04,750
Don't worry. Be careful.

160
00:07:07,110 --> 00:07:08,020
Xiuyu.

161
00:07:09,190 --> 00:07:09,900
Xingfu.

162
00:07:10,950 --> 00:07:12,430
Have the delegates left?

163
00:07:12,430 --> 00:07:13,460
They left quite some time ago.

164
00:07:14,580 --> 00:07:15,750
How did everything go?

165
00:07:16,260 --> 00:07:17,260
Nothing much,

166
00:07:17,630 --> 00:07:19,700
but Mr. Wan was slightly upset.

167
00:07:20,070 --> 00:07:21,260
Why?

168
00:07:22,340 --> 00:07:23,670
Because of my absence?

169
00:07:25,310 --> 00:07:26,870
Are they here to inspect Xingfu Inn

170
00:07:26,870 --> 00:07:27,950
or me?

171
00:07:29,380 --> 00:07:30,630
Fine, I'll pay them a visit.

172
00:07:31,260 --> 00:07:32,630
Where are you going?

173
00:07:32,780 --> 00:07:34,020
I'm going to the Village\hCommittee.

174
00:07:37,990 --> 00:07:39,220
Why was I upset?

175
00:07:40,870 --> 00:07:43,190
Mr. Zhang, the leader of the jury team,

176
00:07:43,460 --> 00:07:44,900
left our village disappointed.

177
00:07:48,630 --> 00:07:50,900
I said this during the pep rally.

178
00:07:51,430 --> 00:07:53,780
The judges' visit to the Wan Village

179
00:07:53,780 --> 00:07:55,950
means a lot to the Wan Village.

180
00:07:57,950 --> 00:07:58,780
We need to show him

181
00:07:58,780 --> 00:08:00,780
what the villagers of the Wan Village are made of.

182
00:08:00,780 --> 00:08:01,750
I also emphasized

183
00:08:01,900 --> 00:08:03,510
that none of you should embarrass me

184
00:08:03,510 --> 00:08:04,870
or the village.

185
00:08:05,070 --> 00:08:08,190
Yet, we were embarrassed.

186
00:08:09,310 --> 00:08:10,900
How dare she?

187
00:08:11,630 --> 00:08:12,750
How dare she leave her position
without permission?

188
00:08:12,750 --> 00:08:14,190
How dare she disregard

189
00:08:14,190 --> 00:08:16,190
our collective interest and honor?

190
00:08:22,110 --> 00:08:23,780
Because of her little achievement,

191
00:08:23,780 --> 00:08:25,700
she thought she is above everyone else.

192
00:08:26,820 --> 00:08:28,670
The person I'm going to reprimand today

193
00:08:28,990 --> 00:08:30,430
is He Xingfu.

194
00:08:31,700 --> 00:08:33,260
Although she is not a member of the CPC,

195
00:08:33,510 --> 00:08:35,460
she is part of the Wan Village.

196
00:08:35,700 --> 00:08:38,140
All for Wan and Wan for All.

197
00:08:38,140 --> 00:08:39,870
It's not just a slogan.

198
00:08:39,870 --> 00:08:41,510
It is a collective idea

199
00:08:42,150 --> 00:08:43,430
that should be instilled in all members
of the Wan Village.

200
00:08:43,430 --> 00:08:45,150
We all need to look at the bigger picture.

201
00:08:50,150 --> 00:08:51,550
Let's take this as a lesson.

202
00:08:52,390 --> 00:08:53,500
Those of you who are present here
are members of the CPC.

203
00:08:54,580 --> 00:08:56,620
If you make the same mistake,

204
00:08:58,220 --> 00:09:00,580
I'll do more than just reprimand you.

205
00:09:03,190 --> 00:09:03,980
You're dismissed.

206
00:09:09,550 --> 00:09:10,620
Remind him to take his medicine.

207
00:09:11,150 --> 00:09:11,620
Sure.

208
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:13,700
Let's go.

209
00:09:26,460 --> 00:09:28,150
Mr. Wan.

210
00:09:28,340 --> 00:09:29,980
I know you're mad at me,

211
00:09:29,980 --> 00:09:31,790
so I came here to explain myself.

212
00:09:32,700 --> 00:09:33,550
Mr. Wan.

213
00:09:33,700 --> 00:09:35,860
12 kids in Shuiwei Village have been diagnosed
with lead poisoning.

214
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:37,860
Lead poisoning?

215
00:09:38,030 --> 00:09:38,860
Yes.

216
00:09:39,030 --> 00:09:40,270
A high level of lead

217
00:09:40,270 --> 00:09:42,670
was found in these 12 kids' blood.

218
00:09:44,670 --> 00:09:46,820
Mr. Wan, lead poisoning can affect

219
00:09:46,820 --> 00:09:48,910
the kids' health and their immune systems.

220
00:09:49,030 --> 00:09:50,860
This will greatly affect the kids' future

221
00:09:50,860 --> 00:09:52,310
and their health.

222
00:09:52,670 --> 00:09:53,500
We can't wait any longer.

223
00:09:53,500 --> 00:09:55,150
We need to find out the source
as soon as possible.

224
00:09:55,950 --> 00:09:57,220
Chuanjia, have you heard about this?

225
00:09:57,580 --> 00:09:58,500
I haven't.

226
00:09:58,500 --> 00:09:59,740
What she just said was news to me too.

227
00:09:59,740 --> 00:10:01,500
Catch up with Maoqin.

228
00:10:01,860 --> 00:10:03,670
Both of you should find out
what actually happened

229
00:10:03,670 --> 00:10:04,100
and report it to me.

230
00:10:04,340 --> 00:10:05,190
Sure.

231
00:10:05,860 --> 00:10:07,390
I'll visit the Shuiwei Village later

232
00:10:07,550 --> 00:10:08,580
to check things out.

233
00:10:08,860 --> 00:10:10,460
I suspect that the well water is polluted.

234
00:10:10,860 --> 00:10:12,790
I've told the officer
of the Environment Monitoring Station

235
00:10:12,790 --> 00:10:13,860
to take some water samples.

236
00:10:16,030 --> 00:10:16,700
All right.

237
00:10:17,430 --> 00:10:19,390
We'll see how things go after we get the results.

238
00:10:23,460 --> 00:10:26,670
Mr. Wan, it's all my fault.

239
00:10:27,390 --> 00:10:27,790
Mr. Wan.

240
00:10:28,190 --> 00:10:28,910
Watch your steps.

241
00:10:31,550 --> 00:10:33,620
I didn't do my job properly.

242
00:10:34,070 --> 00:10:34,740
However,

243
00:10:35,100 --> 00:10:37,070
we had never heard

244
00:10:37,430 --> 00:10:39,100
of lead poisoning before this.

245
00:10:39,310 --> 00:10:40,860
I really have no idea what it is.

246
00:10:41,030 --> 00:10:42,030
I was careless as well.

247
00:10:43,100 --> 00:10:44,310
Which house are we visiting first?

248
00:10:45,100 --> 00:10:47,740
Let's start with Liu's place.

249
00:10:49,740 --> 00:10:52,700
His only grandson is three years old this year.

250
00:10:52,980 --> 00:10:55,820
They discovered a high level of lead in his blood.

251
00:10:56,150 --> 00:10:56,620
Mr. Wan.

252
00:10:57,070 --> 00:10:57,740
Hi.

253
00:11:00,220 --> 00:11:01,190
Where is it?

254
00:11:01,460 --> 00:11:02,620
Right after this turn.

255
00:11:07,620 --> 00:11:08,740
Liu Datou.

256
00:11:10,030 --> 00:11:10,860
Datou.

257
00:11:12,390 --> 00:11:13,030
This is it.

258
00:11:13,950 --> 00:11:14,700
Come on in.

259
00:11:15,860 --> 00:11:16,950
Is anyone home?

260
00:11:16,950 --> 00:11:17,790
Datou.

261
00:11:18,950 --> 00:11:19,550
You're right here.

262
00:11:19,790 --> 00:11:20,790
Come here.

263
00:11:20,980 --> 00:11:23,340
Mr. Wan is here to send you his regards.

264
00:11:24,220 --> 00:11:25,310
Who gave you permission to come here?

265
00:11:25,820 --> 00:11:26,670
Leave now.

266
00:11:26,670 --> 00:11:27,740
Why are you so rude?

267
00:11:27,740 --> 00:11:28,910
Mr. Wan? Who?

268
00:11:28,910 --> 00:11:29,670
I don't know him.

269
00:11:29,820 --> 00:11:32,500
Who am I to talk to a noble man like him?

270
00:11:32,500 --> 00:11:33,190
Get out of here.

271
00:11:33,190 --> 00:11:33,910
Know your place.

272
00:11:33,910 --> 00:11:34,460
Get out of here.

273
00:11:35,310 --> 00:11:36,150
What are you doing?

274
00:11:36,150 --> 00:11:37,620
Cold-blooded freaks.

275
00:11:37,620 --> 00:11:38,670
All you care about is money.

276
00:11:38,670 --> 00:11:39,430
Why...

277
00:11:39,620 --> 00:11:40,460
Mr. Wan is here to send his regards.

278
00:11:40,460 --> 00:11:41,740
I don't care.

279
00:11:42,500 --> 00:11:43,820
His intention is good.

280
00:11:44,950 --> 00:11:45,820
Stop it.

281
00:11:47,860 --> 00:11:48,670
How dare you?

